    "data_size": 248,
    "nom_orig": "Ms.[SP]Saeko",
    "texte_orig": "Is[SP]that[SP]so...![1205][001E][SP]If[SP]you're[SP]that[SP]fired\nup,[SP]I'm[SP]sure[SP]you'll[SP]do[SP]just[SP]fine!\nGood[SP]luck![SP]I'll[SP]be[SP]cheering[SP]for[SP]you!",
